lead_paragraph: Charles had 14 points and 14 rebounds as the Liberty dominated on the glass and secured sole possession of first place in the Eastern Conference heading into the All-Star break.

headline.main: Tina Charles Leads Liberty Past Sparks for Fifth Straight Win
